erstanding bests credit ratings or select a topic below understanding bests credit ratings quick links general comments rating process material sources of informationquality of information opinion type definitions opinion characteristics  identifiers opinion modifiers opinion outlooks opinion affiliation codes bests credit rating scales categories  symbols additional information  important links ambrs code of conduct handling of confidential nonpublic information independence and avoidance of conflicts of interest bests market segment outlook preparing for a rating meeting terms of use use of the am best website and other website disclaimers am best privacy statement ambrs compensation disclosure guide to proper use of bests credit ratings legal  licensing details on the use of am bests trademarks logos and service marks general guide for media  proper use of bests credit ratings and am best rating action press releases am best rating services  propertycasualty this web site needs javascript enabled to work properly please enable it to use the full functionality of the web site thank you am best rating services view bests ratings select ratings type credit ratings advanced search propertycasualty insurance information am best is the leading provider of ratings news analysis and financial information for the propertycasualty insurance industry bests credit ratings are independent opinions regarding the creditworthiness of an issuer or debt obligation bests credit ratings are based on a comprehensive quantitative and qualitative evaluation of a companys balance sheet strength operating performance and business profile or where appropriate the specific nature and details of a debt security view the complete bests credit rating methodology bcrm for details to learn more about am bests propertycasualty ratings and coverage visit the links below search for propertycasualty ratings industry rating services updates view more use our advanced search for more options am best 